FT  05 AUG 94 / UK Company News: Abbey moves up to IPounds 8m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Abbey, the housebuilder in Ireland and the UK, saw a substantial rise in
pre-tax profit from IPounds 2.65m to IPounds 8.14m (Pounds 8.08m) for the
year to April 30.
